1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 29=

3
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:19,839
I've already let you go.

4
00:00:20,199 --> 00:00:21,440
Why are you still following us?

5
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,760
Being a hostage is more comfortable

6
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,879
than staying at the Gate Bureau.

7
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,120
Let me come along.

8
00:00:27,410 --> 00:00:28,239
I'll pay my own way.

9
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:29,990
That won't be necessary.

10
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:33,320
Don't be so quick to say no.

11
00:00:33,719 --> 00:00:34,479
Think about it.

12
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:36,079
Wherever you go now,

13
00:00:36,190 --> 00:00:37,439
you will be pursued and hunted.

14
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:39,679
Having someone of my status around

15
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:42,079
will only benefit you.

16
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:47,119
He has a point.

17
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,079
Exactly.

18
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,280
And how do I know

19
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,200
you're not a mole for the Gate Bureau?

20
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:54,679
Look,

21
00:00:54,759 --> 00:00:56,560
if you suspect me
at any point on the road,

22
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,640
you're free to kill me.

23
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,840
An order from the Commissioner.

24
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:03,439
Catch the Jade Squirrel
and the Sacred Hand Sect members.

25
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,760
Kill them on sight.

26
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,920
Won't we capture them for questioning?

27
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,560
What if Wuxia gets hurt in the process?

28
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:13,099
Are you failing to understand
the Commissioner's orders?

29
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,000
Understood.

30
00:01:17,137 --> 00:01:20,637
(Ministry of Justice)

31
00:01:22,675 --> 00:01:23,787
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

32
00:01:37,425 --> 00:01:40,400
(Chengdu County Border)

33
00:01:41,162 --> 00:01:42,082
We've entered Shu.

34
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:45,079
There should be
a courier station up ahead.

35
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:47,120
We'll stay there tonight.

36
00:01:54,762 --> 00:01:57,175
(Shu Courier Station)

37
00:02:06,410 --> 00:02:07,530
Where is the station master?

38
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,439
Officers,

39
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,759
where have you come from?

40
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:18,840
Vice Minister of Rites Zheng
is retiring and returning home.

41
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,190
He requires lodging for the night.

42
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,240
Forgive me, Vice Minister.

43
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,080
I didn't realize you were arriving.

44
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,039
No need.

45
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:43,919
Come.

46
00:02:51,390 --> 00:02:53,159
Guo Tong,
master of the Shu courier station.

47
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,360
Greetings, Vice Minister.

48
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,680
I've already stepped down from my post.

49
00:02:58,050 --> 00:02:59,919
No need for such formality,
Station Master Guo.

50
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:01,500
We're only staying for a night.

51
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,759
We leave at dawn.

52
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,319
You're too kind, Vice Minister.

53
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,840
Sir, madam,

54
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,680
this way.

55
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,360
It's done.

56
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:28,520
Rong.

57
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,000
If we catch the Jade Squirrel this time,

58
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:33,560
I'll make sure you get your revenge.

59
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,080
Thank you, Wushuang.

60
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:39,000
How has Yu been lately?

61
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,240
I haven't seen him in three or four days.

62
00:03:43,462 --> 00:03:44,103
Yu?

63
00:03:46,275 --> 00:03:48,194
Why wasn't I part of the capture mission?

64
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:51,080
That was the Commissioner's decision.

65
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,400
He knows you're still
grieving for your father,

66
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,319
and he was worried
you might be emotionally unstable.

67
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,759
So why is my sister allowed to go?

68
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,680
Well, Rong is part of the Intel Corps.

69
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,879
She has more experience
tracking criminals.

70
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:09,479
Deputy Luo.

71
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:13,280
I volunteer to lead the squad
that brings in the Jade Squirrel.

72
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:16,079
Yu.

73
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:19,439
I want to hunt this thief by your side,

74
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,079
it's just...

75
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,450
I'm worried you won't be objective.

76
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,639
If that ever happens,

77
00:04:32,175 --> 00:04:33,214
I'll end myself.

78
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:41,560
Fine.

79
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,839
Deputy Luo.

80
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,680
There's a fork in the road ahead.

81
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,920
One path leads to Jiangnan,
the other to Shu.

82
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,190
How should we divide our forces?

83
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:57,959
Rong.

84
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,560
I'll have you lead the men south.

85
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,639
Yu and I will head into Shu.

86
00:05:06,487 --> 00:05:08,480
(Shu Courier Station)

87
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,240
Station Master Guo.

88
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:10,759
Tell your men to get the horses ready.

89
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,120
The Vice Minister is ready to move out.

90
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:16,000
Forgive me, officer.

91
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,639
Two nights ago,

92
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,970
a downpour triggered a landslide.

93
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:21,319
The local officials
are working on it now,

94
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:23,800
but I'm afraid
you won't be able to leave today.

95
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,399
How long will it take?

96
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,879
I've already sent someone to check.

97
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,970
It's not a major collapse.

98
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:30,040
They expect it to be clear by tomorrow.

99
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,120
Alright.

100
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,800
Thank you for the update.

101
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,879
My pleasure, sir.

102
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,120
In that case,

103
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,279
we'll have to stay one more night.

104
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,720
(Shu Courier Station)

105
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,319
Sir!

106
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,199
What is it?

107
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,680
The Gate Bureau is here.

108
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,160
(Token, Ministry of Justice, Field Corps, Luo Wushuang)
We're the Gate Bureau.

109
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,639
My apologies.

110
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,560
I will cooperate fully.

111
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,160
This way.

112
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:19,399
Who has checked
into the station recently?

113
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:22,079
We haven't had many guests lately.

114
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:24,920
Vice Minister Zheng of
the Ministry of Rites is staying here.

115
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,100
He's retiring and going home.

116
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,199
A Vice Minister of Rites?

117
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,040
That's right.

118
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:32,600
He is a high official,
so mind your manners.

119
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,160
- Yes!
- Yes!

120
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,959
Since the Vice Minister is here,

121
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:38,000
we'll all stay on the ground floor.

122
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,680
Yes.

123
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,600
The Vice Minister hasn't left yet?

124
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,560
He was supposed
to leave early this morning,

125
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:46,199
but the heavy rain washed out the road.

126
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:47,380
They're doing repairs now,

127
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:49,519
so it looks like
he'll be here until tomorrow.

128
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,360
The rain washed out the road?

129
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:51,959
Yes.

130
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,160
It looks like

131
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,560
no one is going anywhere.

132
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,360
We're in big trouble.

133
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,950
My cousin is already downstairs

134
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:04,920
with the Gate Bureau.

135
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,160
We're cornered.

136
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:08,319
Can't we just

137
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:09,600
go around the back?

138
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:10,360
No.

139
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:15,279
With the landslide ahead,
everyone knows the road is impassable.

140
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:17,120
If we try to sneak away now,

141
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,000
it'll definitely tip off the Gate Bureau.

142
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:23,920
Actually, I don't think
we need to be this scared.

143
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:26,240
The Gate Bureau wouldn't have the nerve

144
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,519
to mess with a Vice Minister.

145
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:30,680
We'll just stay upstairs today.

146
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,160
Once they head out tomorrow,

147
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,360
then we'll leave.

148
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:34,560
Are you sure about this?

149
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,439
My heart is absolutely racing.

150
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,120
I think he has a point.

151
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,240
So far, the Gate Bureau

152
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,560
haven't set foot upstairs.

153
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,360
That proves

154
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,439
they're also wary of the Vice Minister.

155
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,720
We should keep our cool.

156
00:08:06,090 --> 00:08:07,199
Nothing is going to happen.

157
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:13,079
They are having a feast downstairs.

158
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,560
I haven't eaten all day.

159
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,879
I'm starving.

160
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:28,240
How about I go down
and get us something to eat?

161
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,199
No!

162
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,560
That will arouse suspicion.

163
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:32,559
Indeed.

164
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,120
Wushuang has eyes like a hawk.

165
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,639
You'd be spotted for sure.

166
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,720
Actually,

167
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,720
if we don't show our faces all day,

168
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,559
it'll only make us look guilty.

169
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:44,320
If we just act natural
and go look for food,

170
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,440
they won't suspect a thing.

171
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,759
Zhizhi, I'll go with you.

172
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,679
Be careful.

173
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,000
Cheers! Let's drink!

174
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,519
Eat up.

175
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,770
We still have work to do later.

176
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,770
You haven't had
much of an appetite lately.

177
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,519
Don't let yourself get run down.

178
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,080
The food here in Shu is spicy,

179
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,180
but it really hits the spot.

180
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,840
Here, eat a little more.

181
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,159
I can manage.

182
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,919
Officers,

183
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,159
we haven't seen you

184
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:13,600
all day.

185
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,320
Madam isn't feeling very well,

186
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,600
and the food here doesn't suit her.

187
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,600
We'll cook our own meal.

188
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,559
Of course.

189
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:22,879
The kitchen is right over there.

190
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,320
Thanks for looking out for us.

191
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:34,399
Honestly, I'm glad

192
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,200
we're working together again.

193
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,600
It reminds me

194
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,399
of when we first joined the Gate Bureau.

195
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,279
During our first mission together,

196
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,559
we were so in sync.

197
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:47,200
Yu,

198
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:50,279
I'm the only one
who's truly meant for you.

199
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,240
We belong together.

200
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:51,879
Wushuang.

201
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,279
Let's just eat.

202
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,970
Fine. I'll just watch you eat, then.

203
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,039
Good.

204
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,440
I'm telling you,

205
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:07,120
everything in Shu is spicy.

206
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,519
The old lady craves something sweet.

207
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,919
One has no shame,

208
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,426
and the other is a heartbreaker.

209
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:30,120
I honestly don't know
how you can stand them.

210
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,440
If you'd just listen to me,

211
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,639
I'd use my poison

212
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:34,039
to kill Wushuang

213
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,600
and those cursed constables.

214
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,360
Then, we could just take Mao Buyu and go.

215
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:40,879
Drop it.

216
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,759
Just get the food ready.

217
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:43,580
Don't cause trouble.

218
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,320
See?

219
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:46,639
You never listen to a word I say,

220
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:47,919
which is why you suffer.

221
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,720
How many were with the Vice Minister

222
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,519
when he arrived?

223
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,559
Just the Vice Minister, his wife,

224
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:04,200
a carriage driver, a page boy,

225
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,559
and a servant.

226
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,759
Five?

227
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,200
Yes.

228
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,879
How curious.

229
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,399
Take me up to meet the Vice Minister.

230
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,399
I'd like to pay my respects.

231
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:17,799
But...

232
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:21,879
Right away.

233
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,159
This way, please.

234
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,519
I made all of this myself.

235
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,960
Zhizhi, you're amazing!

236
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:28,960
Of course I am.

237
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,919
Here, madam.

238
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,840
- Eat up.
- It's delicious!

239
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,480
Have some more.

240
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,080
Sir.

241
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,919
Deputy Luo from the Gate Bureau

242
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,840
wishes to pay her respects
to the Vice Minister.

243
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:59,039
The Vice Minister has retired.

244
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,159
He values his peace.

245
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:00,960
That's all.

246
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:12,559
I'll pay my respects and leave.

247
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,519
I won't be a bother.

248
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:17,759
You've already disturbed him.

249
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:21,039
Why is the Vice Minister
so reluctant to see me?

250
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:23,559
Is there something inconvenient?

251
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,480
Who is it?

252
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:30,080
Vice Minister, it's Deputy Luo
from the Gate Bureau.

253
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:31,879
She'd like to pay her respects.

254
00:12:35,759 --> 00:12:38,120
I'm no longer a Vice Minister.

255
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:40,679
There's no need
for the Gate Bureau to pay respects.

256
00:12:42,620 --> 00:12:44,480
The Vice Minister has
served our country well.

257
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,440
I'll pay my respects and go.

258
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:51,960
Fine, come in.

259
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,240
Have you eaten yet?

260
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:13,710
I, Luo Wushuang, Deputy
of the Gate Bureau's Field Corps,

261
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,240
pay respects to the Vice Minister.

262
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:24,000
I'm no longer a Vice Minister.

263
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:26,559
Don't be so formal, Deputy Luo.

264
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:29,840
The Vice Minister
isn't feeling well today.

265
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:31,639
If there's nothing else, Deputy Luo,

266
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,480
please leave.

267
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:36,879
Perhaps you haven't heard,
Vice Minister.

268
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:40,279
My grandfather is Luo Shixun,
Commissioner of the Gate Bureau.

269
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:43,120
He was very close with Minister Hu.

270
00:13:43,399 --> 00:13:44,279
Grandfather often said

271
00:13:44,399 --> 00:13:46,919
that Minister Hu spoke of you
with the highest praise.

272
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:50,159
You must be mistaken, Deputy Luo.

273
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,519
The Minister's surname is Wu,

274
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,559
not Hu.

275
00:13:58,279 --> 00:13:59,120
Yes. My mistake.

276
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,039
I will take my leave.

277
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,679
How did I slip up?

278
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:31,000
Zheng Yi, Vice Minister of Rites,
lost his wife the year before last.

279
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,320
Three years later,
he married a new wife.

280
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:36,320
He was even impeached
by the Censorate for it.

281
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,510
The woman he took as his new wife

282
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,879
is nearly thirty years younger
than he is.

283
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,639
Hence, the secrecy.

284
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:53,559
Stop!

285
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,440
My men are all downstairs.

286
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,440
You have nowhere to run.

287
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,919
That makes things even easier.

288
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,840
I'll have to trouble you
to escort us out.

289
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,120
Wushuang!

290
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,879
I was counting on you to save me!

291
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,080
How did you get caught too?

292
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:27,600
Shut up.

293
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:28,279
You useless fool.

294
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,120
Make way!

295
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,519
Or I will kill her.

296
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,120
Go now.

297
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:36,000
No, we leave together or not at all.

298
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,639
I am staying here with you.

299
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:39,639
No. I can handle this myself.

300
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:40,759
Go!

301
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,000
No one leaves!

302
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:54,039
Yu...

303
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,600
Yunchang.

304
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,399
Release Wushuang.

305
00:16:03,879 --> 00:16:06,279
Let my family go first,
and then I'll let her go.

306
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,639
Buyu, don't let them go!

307
00:16:10,639 --> 00:16:11,519
Don't listen to her!

308
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:20,919
Let their family leave first.

309
00:16:21,159 --> 00:16:21,799
Yu!

310
00:16:22,519 --> 00:16:23,200
Step aside.

311
00:16:26,639 --> 00:16:27,200
Go! Quickly!

312
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,200
I'm not leaving!

313
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,000
Go!

314
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:41,519
Yunchang.

315
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,000
I have let your family leave.

316
00:16:44,519 --> 00:16:45,799
Release Wushuang immediately.

317
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,080
Drop all your weapons.

318
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,240
Back into the corner.

319
00:16:49,759 --> 00:16:50,600
Don't listen to her!

320
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:00,279
Drop them!

321
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:02,919
Yu, don't do this.

322
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,039
No!

323
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,839
Everyone, get out!

324
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,640
You too!

325
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:22,519
Yu, no!

326
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,599
Yu, do not let her escape!

327
00:17:30,519 --> 00:17:31,240
Yu!

328
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:44,839
Yu.

329
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,599
Avenge me.

330
00:17:50,519 --> 00:17:51,200
Wushuang!

331
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,079
Chang!

332
00:18:04,599 --> 00:18:06,960
I...

333
00:18:14,012 --> 00:18:17,287
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

334
00:18:17,325 --> 00:18:20,200
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

335
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:26,418
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

336
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:30,920
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

337
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:33,970
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

338
00:18:35,138 --> 00:18:40,378
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

339
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,993
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

340
00:18:43,993 --> 00:18:47,643
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

341
00:18:47,712 --> 00:18:51,202
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

342
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:54,275
♪To the ends of time♪

343
00:18:54,275 --> 00:18:57,650
♪The moon traces your face♪

344
00:18:57,837 --> 00:19:01,425
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

345
00:19:01,425 --> 00:19:07,665
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

346
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:11,215
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

347
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:15,038
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

348
00:19:15,325 --> 00:19:18,350
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

349
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:21,450
♪On our way to forever♪

350
00:19:21,450 --> 00:19:25,300
♪The moon traces your face♪

351
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:28,660
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

352
00:19:28,850 --> 00:19:34,810
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

353
00:19:35,887 --> 00:19:45,527
♪Just to be with you♪
